  .section.s4.dark-gray(data-destination="products")
    .row
      .small-12.columns
        p.lead Orikami builds custom data products. Data products are not about the data, but about discovery and covert action. Data should get out of our way. With our partners we build products that deliver real-time insights, make accurate prediction and behave as smart sensors. 
    .row
