  .section.s2b
    .row
      .small-12.columns
        h1 How can we be of service for you?
    .row(data-equalizer)
      .medium-6.columns
        object.sm.svg-image(type="image/svg+xml" data="images/ins3.svg")
        h3 Data Lab
        p Data is the new oil. If you are sitting on a "big data deposit", you probably know it can bring a lot of wealth. However, do you know how to drill that deposit? Do you know how to refine the data for interesting patterns and couple rich data sources? Is your culture ready to un-silo its data? We know how to kickstart your endeavours! Together, we setup a data lab. We investigate your data information quality. We help you setup your data wells and exploit your data fields.
      .medium-6.columns
        object.sm.svg-image(type="image/svg+xml" data="images/learn3.svg")
        h3 Data products
        p Crude oil cannot be used. Petroleum has to be refined to create fuels and plastics. The same with data. Unrefined data is meaningless. Data products are the result of a process of refining data. We build data products and tailor them to your specific needs. We have a very flexible process to deliver fast and with high quality.
        p See our process? See our portfolio / example products / Contact us

